title: GPT-4.5 achieves 89% on SWE-bench Verified
summary: Our latest model GPT-4.5 has achieved state-of-the-art performance on the SWE-bench Verified benchmark, solving 89% of real-world software engineering tasks.

title: Claude 3.5 Sonnet: New reasoning capabilities
summary: Claude 3.5 Sonnet demonstrates improved performance on GPQA Diamond, achieving 71% accuracy on graduate-level scientific reasoning questions.

title: Gemini 2.0: Multimodal breakthrough
summary: Google DeepMind announces Gemini 2.0 with enhanced agentic capabilities, showing 65% success rate on WebArena benchmark.

title: Meta announces 10^26 FLOP training run
summary: Meta AI completes first 10^26 FLOP training run using new distributed training infrastructure across 50,000 H100 GPUs.

title: Mistral releases Mistral Large 2
summary: Mistral Large 2 achieves competitive performance on coding benchmarks with 78% on HumanEval and strong multilingual capabilities.
